import React from "react";

function Lasers() {
  return (
    <svg class = "painting"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsOsb="http://www.openswatchbook.org/uri/2009/osb"
      width="3550.584"
      height="2892.394"
      version="1.1"
      viewBox="0 0 3550.583 2892.394"
    >
      <defs>
        <linearGradient osbPaint="solid">
          <stop offset="0" stopColor="#dbd2c9" stopOpacity="1"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        <filter
          id="filter1422"
          width="1"
          height="1"
          x="0"
          y="0"
          colorInterpolationFilters="sRGB"
        >
          <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="0.001"></feGaussianBlur>
        </filter>
      </defs>
      <g
        strokeDasharray="none"
        strokeMiterlimit="4"
        strokeOpacity="1"
        display="inline"
        transform="translate(-3665.21 -705.78)"
      >
        <path
